1. Books
purpose: stores the book details
primary key: book_isbn (unique integer for each book)

2.Authors
purpose: stores authors information
primary key: author_id (auto_generated)

3.Borrowers
purpose: stores borrowers details
primary key: borrower_id

4. BookAuthors (Junction Table)
purpose: resolves the many-to-many relationship between books and authors
composite primary key: book_isbn, author_id

5. BookBorrowers (Junction Table)
purpose: tracks book loans -resolves many-to-many relationship between books and borrowers
primary key: borrow_id
